"                        \"content of my file\".getBytes(), \"text/plain\")\n"
"                .addAttachment(\"my-file-2.txt\",\n"
"                        new File(\"my-file.txt\"), \"text/plain\")\n"
"        );\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/main/guides/mailer-reference.adoc:125
